article.headline: Moore scores 20 to lead Drexel to 70-60 victory over Delaware
article.description: — Justin Moore had 20 points in Drexel's 70-60 victory over Delaware on Monday night.
article.linkText: Moore scores 20 to lead Drexel to 70-60 victory over Delaware
article.story: NEWARK, Del. -- — Justin Moore had 20 points in Drexel's 70-60 victory over Delaware on Monday night. Moore shot 8 for 15, including 2 for 5 from beyond the arc for the Dragons (18-11, 11-5 Coastal Athletic Association). Amari Williams added 14 points and 11 rebounds. Lucas Moore totaled 13 points and six boards. Christian Ray led the way for the Fightin' Blue Hens (17-12, 9-7) with 12 points, 12 rebounds and two steals. Jyare Davis added 11 points and two blocks. Niels Lane scored 10. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
